      <title>巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗的律师称，他敦促国际货币基金组织进行选举审计</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-urges-imf-call-election-audit-his-lawyer-says-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦被监禁的前总理伊姆兰·汗 (Imran Khan) 的律师周四表示，他将写信给国际货币基金组织，敦促其对该国颇具争议的 2 月 8 日全国选举进行独立审计，然后再继续与伊斯兰堡进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-ex-pm-imran-khan-urges-imf-call-election-audit-his-lawyer-says-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:48:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>VinFast第四季度亏损扩大，有信心实现2024年销售目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vinfast-posts-higher-revenue-fourth-quarter-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南电动汽车 (EV) 制造商 VinFast 周四表示，其第四季度净亏损较前三个月扩大了 3.4%，但随着其向新市场扩张，该公司今年的目标是使汽车销量增加近两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vinfast-posts-higher-revenue-fourth-quarter-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:42:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国议会一读批准放宽渔业规则</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-parliament-approves-looser-fisheries-rules-first-reading-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国议会周四一致投票决定放松对渔业的监管，以回应其价值数十亿美元的海鲜行业对当前规定过于严厉的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-parliament-approves-looser-fisheries-rules-first-reading-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:59:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沮丧的韩国患者敦促解决医生的抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dismayed-south-korean-patients-urge-resolution-doctors-protest-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[实习医生大规模罢工三天后，韩国患者周四表达了越来越多的担忧和沮丧，因为全国各地的医院推迟了手术，急诊室拒绝接受患者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dismayed-south-korean-patients-urge-resolution-doctors-protest-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:27:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grab 预计 2024 年营收将在盈利季度和回购计划后疲弱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/grab-unveils-first-ever-share-buyback-after-profitable-quarter-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Grab Holdings 周四公布了有史以来的首个季度盈利，并宣布了首次股票回购计划，但疲软的年度销售预测引发了增长担忧，并打压了这家拼车和食品配送公司的股价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/grab-unveils-first-ever-share-buyback-after-profitable-quarter-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯缺席航展，防务公司看到亚洲机遇</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/defence-firms-see-asia-opportunity-russian-absence-air-show-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[专家和业内消息人士称，俄罗斯公司因应对制裁和维持对乌克兰的入侵而苦苦挣扎，因此缺席新加坡航展，这表明俄罗斯的竞争对手有机会介入一些亚洲客户的事务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/defence-firms-see-asia-opportunity-russian-absence-air-show-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:18:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚在首次大规模龙卷风袭击后进行调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-investigates-after-first-large-scale-tornado-strikes-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府官员称，印度尼西亚遭遇龙卷风袭击，其规模此前从未有过记录，造成至少 33 人受伤，建筑物受损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-investigates-after-first-large-scale-tornado-strikes-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国商飞在新加坡航展上抢走了空客和波音的风头</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-upstages-airbus-boeing-singapore-airshow-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司本周在新加坡航展上抢走了行业领头羊空客和波音公司的风头，展示了其自主研发的C919和ARJ21喷气式飞机，同时寻求国际认证和外国订单。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-upstages-airbus-boeing-singapore-airshow-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:23:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司的可持续发展口号掩盖了对绿色未来的分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/airlines-sustainability-mantra-masks-divides-over-green-future-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，活动组织者在宣传新加坡航展时被问及今年的航空和国防盛会有何不同。 “可持续性，可持续性，可持续性，”他回答道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/airlines-sustainability-mantra-masks-divides-over-green-future-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:16:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国外相本月将在美国会见布林肯</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-foreign-minister-meet-blinken-us-this-month-2024-02-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国外交部周四表示，韩国外交部长赵太烈将于 2 月 28 日访问美国并与外长安东尼·布林肯举行会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-foreign-minister-meet-blinken-us-this-month-2024-02-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 06:35:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
